Using git

- Ignore .DS_Store in git

    git config --global core.excludesfile ~/.gitignore

    echo .DS_Store >> ~/.gitignore

- Set editor for git

   git config --global core.editor vim

- (Optional) Use GitHub GUI for convenience

  http://mac.github.com/

  do check diff before commit.


Coding Style

- Release an object in dealloc function:

    if you declare a "retain" object, e.g. "@property (retain) UIView *view;"

    call "self.view = nil" to release the object and avoid dangling pointer.

- Do not use "autorelease" if possible.

- Do not use IBOutlet if possible.


